<div class="instruction"><strong><u>Undo</u></strong><br>
<A NAME="undo"> </A>
<P>Allows you to step back to any previous model (List 5) stored in the DSC
file. All models are stored unless you PURGE the DSC datafile, or
explicitly delete them using this dialog.
<P>Note: If you use the GUIDE, and automatic purge occurs after you have
checked for extinction - any models marked explicilty as 'to be retained'
will not be PURGED.<BR>

</div>
